s present.</s></p><p class="description"><s>No recorded pathogenicity to man, guinea pig, mouse, rat, or rabbit.</s></p><p class="description"><s>Mesophilic: optimal temperature, 37 C; upper limit, 48 C.</s></p><p class="description"><s>DNA: 45.5% guanine + cytosine.</s></p><p class="description"><s>Cytochrome: of the protohem class.</s></p><p class="description"><s>Anaerobic.</s></p><p class="description"><s>Habitat: rumen contents of sheep.</s></p></content></protolog>